title: Things to know about Hollywood leading lady Maureen O'Hara
text: Things to know about Hollywood leading lady Maureen O'Hara By Associated Press | October 24, 2015 @ 12:50 pm FILE - This Nov. 8, 2014 file photo Maureen O'Hara arrives at the 6th annual Governors Awards at the Hollywood and Highland Center in Los Angeles. O'Hara,who appeared in such classic films as "The Quiet Man" and How Green Was My Valley," has died. Her manager says O'Hara died in her sleep Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015 at her home in Boise, Idaho. (Photo by Chris Pizzello/Invision/AP, File)
